<a class="title" href="/nodes/97201/comments/1426570">Licence</a>
</h2>
<p class="meta">
Posté par <a href="/users/zenitram" rel="author">Zenitram</a> (<a href="http://mediaarea.net">page perso</a>) <time class="updated" datetime="2013-01-25T22:56:54+01:00"><span class="date">le 25/01/13</span> <span class="time">à 22:56</span></time>.
